de.fhg.iml.vlog.xfvrp.report
Class Event

java.lang.Object
  de.fhg.iml.vlog.xfvrp.report.Event

public class Event
extends java.lang.Object

The Event is the atomic structure of a report and represents the visit of a truck at a certain node. The values in a event are not cummulative, so the summary objects contain the summed values. Events are built up in the simulation process, when report object is requested in the solution object.

Author:
hschneid
